sequenceDiagram
    actor S as Student
    participant FE as Frontend React
    participant MW as Auth Middleware
    participant PC as PDF Controller
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant KIT as PDFKit
    S->>FE: Click Download PDF Report
    FE->>MW: GET /api/v1/pdf/generate JWT
    MW->>MW: Verify JWT
    MW->>PC: Forward Request
    PC->>DB: Fetch Latest ResumeAnalysis
    PC->>DB: Fetch Latest TestResult
    DB-->>PC: Analysis and Test Data
    PC->>KIT: Build PDF Document
    KIT->>KIT: Add Scores Skills Feedback Plan
    KIT-->>PC: PDF Buffer
    PC-->>FE: Stream PDF as application/pdf
    FE-->>S: Browser downloads PDF file
